  "synopsis": "Full of confidence after drawing the Heavenly Sword, Shen Jianxin descended the mountain and returned to the martial world. Meanwhile, the Central Plains martial arts world faced an unprecedented crisis. Bearing the power of his birth chart and the Heavenly Sword, Shen Jianxin was tasked with a perilous mission to enter the world of seafaring, becoming embroiled in layers of intrigue. During his journey, unexpected events occurred one after another, and the identities of mysterious figures were gradually revealed…\n\n(Source: Bilibili, translated)",
